        <div class="why-item"><h3>Vacation rental priority</h3><p>A broken appliance in a rental property is lost revenue. We work with Dana Point property managers on short-notice repairs. Call us &mdash; we'll tell you what we can do and when.</p></div>
        <div class="why-item"><h3>Luxury brands stocked</h3><p>Sub-Zero, Wolf, Miele, Thermador, Viking, U-Line &mdash; our OC technicians carry OEM parts for the brands common in Monarch Beach and the harbor-view estates. Most calls finish same visit.</p></div>
        <div class="why-item"><h3>90-day warranty, no exceptions</h3><p>Every repair carries a 90-day warranty on parts and labor. If the same issue returns, we come back at no charge.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="city-reviews">
    <div class="city-reviews-inner">
