      <div class="reviews-grid">
        <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p>"Sub-Zero in our Monarch Beach home failing. Same Day came out, cleaned the coils &mdash; completely coated with salt residue &mdash; and replaced the fan motor. Told us it needed service every 6 months given the location. Nobody had ever mentioned this. Running perfectly."</p><div class="review-author">&mdash; Catherine W., Monarch Beach</div></div>
        <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p>"We manage vacation rentals in Dana Point. Same Day is our go-to for appliance issues. They pick up, they show up, and they're done in one visit. That's all we need."</p><div class="review-author">&mdash; Pacific Coast Property Management, Dana Point</div></div>
        <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p>"Wolf range burners failing on our Headlands home. Technician replaced the electrodes, explained why coastal homes need annual checks, and was done in 90 minutes. Excellent service."</p><div class="review-author">&mdash; James P., Strand at Headlands</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="city-pricing">
    <div class="city-pricing-inner">
      <h2>Repair Pricing in Dana Point</h2>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card"><div class="pricing-label">Diagnostic Fee</div><div class="pricing-price">$89</div><div class="pricing-note">Credited toward repair &middot; Written estimate &middot; Coastal maintenance guidance included</div></div>
        <div class="pricing-card"><div class="pricing-label">Standard Repair</div><div class="pricing-price">$150&ndash;$350</div><div class="pricing-note">Parts + labor &middot; OEM parts &middot; 90-day warranty</div></div>
        <div class="pricing-card"><div class="pricing-label">Luxury Brand Repair</div><div class="pricing-price">$250&ndash;$600+</div><div class="pricing-note">Sub-Zero, Wolf, Miele, Thermador &middot; OEM parts</div></div>
        <div class="pricing-card highlight"><div class="pricing-label">Warranty</div><div class="pricing-price">90 Days</div><div class="pricing-note">All repairs &middot; Parts &amp; labor &middot; No-charge callback</div></div>
